<br>
<br>
You might try a DeMarini Chute Trainer. I've heard good things about them and I'm thinking about getting one:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.sportsnmore.com/baseball/training/chute_trainer.asp" target="top">Chute Trainer</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
