I have a Wilson Easy Toss. It has a rechargeable battery so you can take it anywhere to hit without an extension cord. It lobs up balls about 5 feet hit just like softtoss...throws baseballs or softballs. Tosses one every 15 seconds or so. You can hit them into a backstop or set it up like a pitcher and hit them into the field. Works good and gets a lot of swings in quick. Better than a bad batting practice pitcher like me. lol<br>
